      "text": [
        " : \"شَهَادَةُ اَلصِّبْيَانِ جَائِزَةٌ بَيْنَهُمْ مَا لَمْ يَتَفَرَّقُوا أَوْ يَرْجِعُوا إِلَى أَهْلِيهِمْ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3294 - And it was narrated from Talhah ibn Zayd, from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as), from his father Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), from his forefathers, from Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as), who said:\n\"The testimony of children is valid among them as long as they have not dispersed or returned to their families.\""
        ]
      }
    },
